With pyRenamer you can change the name of several files at the same time
easily.

→ You can use patterns to rename files.  → You can use search & replace to
rename files.  → You can use common substitutions.  → You can manually
rename selected files.  → You can rename images using their metadata.
→ You can rename music using its metadata.
